♫  I stop, yet I've never said goodbye to the past  ♫

158
00:17:33,040 --> 00:17:35,480
♫  Mourning as I watch you leave, the sadness never ceases  ♫

159
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:38,160
♫  Tears of regret, pain running deep  ♫

160
